These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, peach, orange, zucchini
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, gospel, dubstep, hip-hop
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, argentine, malaysian, italian
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, cat, fish, mouse
 1. the fan of indie is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
 2. the person eating pomegranate is in an even position##4
 3. the japanese is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
 4. the malaysian is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
 5. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
 6. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 7. the argentine is the person eating orange##1
 8. the owner of the fish is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the mouse and the fan of hip-hop##2
10. the person eating pomegranate is the owner of the mouse##1
11. the fan of dubstep is the person eating zucchini##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | orange  | pomegranate    | zucchini    | peach   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | indie   | dubstep       | hip-hop    |
| Nationality   | argentine | japanese | italian    | malaysian |
| Pet           | cat | mouse       | goldfish | fish     |

