.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: papaya, strawberry, spinach, onion
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, video-games, puzzles, camping
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, german, indonesian, italian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, badminton, golf, tennis
 1. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
 2. the german is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
 4. the person eating strawberry is the brazilian##1
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 6. the brazilian is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
 7. the person eating onion is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
 8. the italian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
 9. the indonesian is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating spinach is in an odd position##4
11. the indonesian is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | papaya  | strawberry    | spinach     | onion       |
| Hobby         | puzzles | camping | writing   | video-games |
| Nationality   | indonesian | brazilian   | german   | italian    |
| Sport         | golf | tennis  | handball | badminton   |

