.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, tea, coffee
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, mechanic, manager, entrepreneur
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, brazilian, canadian, american
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, fish, snake
 1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the journalist##3
 2. the brazilian is the manager##1
 3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 4. the journalist is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 5. the person drinking milk is the entrepreneur##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 7. the owner of the goldfish is the american##1
 8. the entrepreneur is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking tea is on the left of the malaysian##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is the person drinking tea##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade | tea   | coffee    | milk      |
| Job           | manager | journalist | mechanic | entrepreneur     |
| Nationality   | brazilian      | american   | malaysian   | canadian |
| Pet           | snake         | goldfish       | fish  | pony       |

