.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, juice, coffee, tea
There 4 different types of food: potato, peas, broccoli, pomegranate
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, baking, puzzles, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, climbing, skiing, water-polo
 1. the person drinking lemonade is the person eating potato##1
 2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 3. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
 4. the person who's hobby is baking is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking juice is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 8. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
 9. the person who's sport is skiing is the person who's hobby is baking##1
10. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
11. the person drinking coffee is the person eating pomegranate##1
12. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | tea       | coffee   | lemonade   | juice   |
| Food       | peas        | pomegranate | potato    | broccoli       |
| Hobby      | skydiving | baking    | puzzles  | camping |
| Sport      | climbing  | skiing  | rowing | water-polo    |

