.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, radish, watermelon, pepper
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, traveling, photography, board-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, freelancer, paramedic, project-manager
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, baseball, badminton, rowing
 1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person eating pepper##2
 3. the paramedic is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 4. the freelancer is the person eating lime##1
 5. the nurse is on the left or right of the freelancer##3
 6. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating radish is the nurse##1
 8. the person who's hobby is photography is the freelancer##1
 9. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
10. the freelancer is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
11. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person eating watermelon##3
12. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | watermelon    | pepper      | lime          | radish    |
| Hobby   | traveling | board-games       | photography | fishing |
| Job     | project-manager     | paramedic      | freelancer     | nurse |
| Sport   | baseball   | rowing | badminton        | biathlon   |

