.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk, sprite, cola
There 4 different types of food: lemon, blueberry, apricot, grapefruit
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, ambient, soul, blues
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, polish, australian, egyptian
 1. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 2. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 3. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 5. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of blues is between the australian and the fan of ambient##2
 7. the fan of soul is the person eating apricot##1
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is the person eating apricot##1
 9. the polish is on the far right##1
10. the dutch is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage      | sprite  | soy-milk    | juice       | cola       |
| Food          | grapefruit    | apricot | blueberry | lemon     |
| Music-Genre   | trance | soul        | blues    | ambient   |
| Nationality   | dutch  | australian      | egyptian    | polish |

