 1. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 2. the indian is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 4. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the mexican##3
 5. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 6. the chinese is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 8. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
 9. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
10. the brazilian is on the far right##1
11. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
12. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | action    | superhero  | time-travel      |
| Nationality   | mexican      | chinese | indian | brazilian   |
| Pet           | rat       | goldfish | hamster   | pony       |
