 4. the person watching thriller movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the brazilian is on the right of the indonesian##1
 6. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
 7. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the canadian##1
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the indian and the person watching time-travel movies##2
10. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
12. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3

