The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, baseball, weightlifting, biathlon
 1. the person eating banana is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
 3. the fan of blues is between the person watching superhero movies and the person who's sport is baseball##2
 4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 5. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
 6. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person eating lime##1
 7. the fan of classical is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person watching superhero movies##1
 9. the person eating blueberry is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
11. the person eating blueberry is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan of trance is on the left of the person eating lime##1
13. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
