The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, baseball, climbing, ice-hockey
 1. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
 2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the pilot is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is handball##2
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the canadian##1
 5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person drinking mirinda##1
 6. the thai is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
 8. the canadian is on the right of the thai##1
 9. the security-guard is on the left of the pilot##1
10. the coach is in an even position##4
11. the british is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |       3        |       4       |
