 6. the person watching musical movies is in an odd position##4
 7. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
 8. the nigerian is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
 9. the fan of classical is in an even position##4
10. the fan of country is between the person watching musical movies and the brazilian##2
11. the chinese is on the right of the fan of country##1
12. the nigerian is on the left or right of the chinese##3

.:: Answer ::.
