The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, hiking, reading, camping
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, romance, action
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, climbing, cricket, biathlon
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 3. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the person watching drama movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
10. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
11. the person watching action movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | fanta       | mirinda | iced-tea        | almond-milk        |
| Hobby         | camping | reading       | rock-climbing | hiking |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | drama        | documentary    | romance      |
| Sport         | climbing     | cricket    | biathlon | lacrosse   |

