.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, rock, hip-hop, trance
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, turkish, malaysian, german
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, cricket, swimming, sailing
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, bus, boat, trike
 1. the fan of trance is the person who's sport is swimming##1
 2. the person who's sport is swimming is between the nigerian and the german##2
 3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
 4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the turkish##1
 5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 6. the fan of rock is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
 8. the german is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
10. the nigerian is in an even position##4
11. the nigerian is on the far right##1
12. the fan of gospel is on the right of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | rock      | gospel | trance     | hip-hop        |
| Nationality   | malaysian | german  | turkish     | nigerian |
| Sport         | cricket    | lacrosse | swimming      | sailing |
| Transport     | trike | bus     | boat | van       |

 